Manchester City made their first approach for Riyad Mahrez two weeks ago, giving Leicester time to identify a replacement. Mahrez knows this and is determined to express his dissatisfaction at Leicester blocking a move. [RMC Sport]<br />
<br />
Pep on Mahrez: &quot;We tried to do it in the summertime, we tried to do it now, but like summer, they locked the door and we can go to the summer and holidays. It was not possible. With Laporte yes, with the other one no. We are going to see what happens in the summer.&quot;
